<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1342] Tags not fully preserved when merging PDFs.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1342</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When merging PDFs, 508 accessibility tags are only preserved on the first page of combined PDF.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Both PDFMergerUtility.mergeDocuments() and PDFMergerUtility..appendDocument() exhibit this behavior.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example file attached to BugZilla &quot;issue&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Java 1.6.0_26, PDFMergerUtility.</environment>
